> 
> Megatron turned to Blindchaos and Dominjoe. "The tour will have to 
wait,
> I have urgent things to attend to." he told them, then headed 
towards
> the elevator. "I can however use your help." he told them.


::BLINDCHAOS AND DOMNIJOE::

    Blindchaos let out one off his biggest, most cheerful grins.
    "Hey..no problem, boss." he said. "Work before pleasure!"
    Domnijoe saluted respectfully to her commander.
    "And we would be honored to help."
    The two of them remained quiet as their leader delt with incomming 
messages and grew angry with Havotron's threat toward their leader. 
Domnijoe snarled.
    "The nerve of some idiots" she spat. She looked at Megatron. "I 
will follow you the day I die. You have never failed me and you have 
never failed yor troops. To that I seal my loyalty!!"
    Blindchaos simply rolled his optics at the femme's speech.

Northlight
